.modal.fade#rsvp-success-modal
  .modal-dialog.modal-sm
    .modal-content
      .modal-body
        | Thanks! Your RSVP has been saved.
      .modal-footer.text-center
        button.btn.btn-dark(type='button',data-dismiss='modal',aria-hidden='true') Ok
.modal.fade#rsvp-error-modal
  .modal-dialog.modal-sm
    .modal-content
      .modal-body
        | There was an error saving your RSVP.<br><br>
        | If you've already RSVP'd, please <a href="/guests/login">Login</a>.<br><br>
        | If not, make sure that you've entered your name and 
        | that your password is at least 6 characters long.
      .modal-footer.text-center
        button.btn.btn-dark(type='button',data-dismiss='modal',aria-hidden='true') Ok
.modal.fade#edit-error-modal
  .modal-dialog.modal-sm
    .modal-content
      .modal-body
        | There was an error saving your RSVP.<br><br>
        | Please make sure the data you've entered is valid.
      .modal-footer.text-center
        button.btn.btn-dark(type='button',data-dismiss='modal',aria-hidden='true') Ok
