  .modal-dialog.modal-sm
    .modal-content
      .modal-body
        | Unable to login, please make sure your email and password are correct.
      .modal-footer.text-center
        button.btn.btn-dark(type='button',data-dismiss='modal',aria-hidden='true') Ok
.modal.fade#confirm-delete-modal
  .modal-dialog.modal-sm
    .modal-content
      .modal-body
        | Are you sure you want to delete this guest from the list?
      .modal-footer.text-center
        button.btn.btn-dark.btn-ok(type='button',data-dismiss='modal',aria-hidden='true') Delete
        button.btn.btn-cancel(type='button',data-dismiss='modal',aria-hidden='true') Cancel